{"id":324861,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/12/【图说天朝】上海雾霾严重：pm2-5指数破600/","date":"2013-12-06T09:17:43Z","modified":"2015-03-29T09:15:16Z","title":"【图说天朝】上海雾霾严重：PM2.5指数破600","content":"<p>@央视新闻：今天（12月6日）13时最新数据，PM2.5爆表后继续扬升，目前上海全市平均602.5；PM10平均浓度671.0，最高的普陀监测站已达726.0。据气象部门介绍，目前上海市各项指标和条件符合发布霾红色预警。网友：真的不敢呼吸了。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/12/Bax7aBYCcAAe8Ex.jpg-large.jpeg\"><img class=\" wp-image-324862\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/12/Bax7aBYCcAAe8Ex.jpg-large.jpeg\" alt=\"Bax7aBYCcAAe8Ex.jpg-large\" width=\"350\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/12/Bax7aBYCcAAe8Ex.jpg-large.jpeg 506w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/12/Bax7aBYCcAAe8Ex.jpg-large-169x300.jpeg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">上海雾霾图片  更多<a href=\"http://news.163.com/photoview/00AN0001/40729.html#p=9FE0AEQ500AN0001\" target=\"_blank\">内容</a></p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-2 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-2' class='gallery galleryid-324861 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/12/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e4%b8%8a%e6%b5%b7%e9%9b%be%e9%9c%be%e4%b8%a5%e9%87%8d%ef%bc%9apm2-5%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b0%e7%a0%b4600/9fe0af3t00an0001/'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/12/9FE0AF3T00AN0001-150x150.jpg\" clas